Package: srscod
Title: India SRS Causes of Death Statistics 2021-2023
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Moumita", "Saha", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tidy datasets and analytical functions from the Sample
    Registration System (SRS) Causes of Death Report 2021-2023, published by
    the Office of the Registrar General of India (ORGI). Covers 1,59,296 coded
    deaths across 28 states and 8 UTs, classified under 63 ICD-10 cause
    categories. Functions support stratified queries by sex, age group, state
    category (EAG+Assam vs Other States), residence (Rural/Urban), and
    geographic zone.
